description: Have you ever wondered how many meters are in one swimming length or vice versa. By using the Swimming Lengths Conversion you can calculate how meters you are swimming based on the number of lengths or how many lengths you have swam based on the number of meters.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask swimming lengths conversion to convert ten lengths to meters
Alexa, ask swimming lengths conversion to convert five hundred meters to lengths
name: Swimming Lengths Conversion
shortDescription: Swimming Lengths, Convert from Lengths to Meters & Meters to Swimming Lengths
